<li id="cite_note-:26-18"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-:26_18-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-:26_18-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-:26_18-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-:26_18-3"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFHales2019" class="citation journal cs1">Hales, Brian C. (2019). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://byustudies.byu.edu/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/58-3halessecured.pdf">"Naturalistic Explanations of the Origin of the Book of Mormon: A Longitudinal Study"</a> <span class="cs1-format">(PDF)</span>. <i><a href="/wiki/BYU_Studies_Quarterly" class="mw-redirect" title="BYU Studies Quarterly">BYU Studies Quarterly</a></i>. <b>58</b> (3): 105–148. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://ghostarchive.org/archive/20221009/https://byustudies.byu.edu/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/58-3halessecured.pdf">Archived</a> <span class="cs1-format">(PDF)</span> from the original on 2022-10-09.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=BYU+Studies+Quarterly&amp;rft.atitle=Naturalistic+Explanations+of+the+Origin+of+the+Book+of+Mormon%3A+A+Longitudinal+Study&amp;rft.volume=58&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.pages=105-148&amp;rft.date=2019&amp;rft.aulast=Hales&amp;rft.aufirst=Brian+C.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbyustudies.byu.edu%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2F58-3halessecured.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABook+of+Mormon" class="Z3988"></span></span>
