<li id="cite_note-FOOTNOTEDavis2020165–168-25"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-FOOTNOTEDavis2020165–168_25-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFDavis2020">Davis 2020</a>, pp.&#160;165–168.</span>
