<li id="cite_note-FOOTNOTEHardy2003631-57"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-FOOTNOTEHardy2003631_57-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-FOOTNOTEHardy2003631_57-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFHardy2003">Hardy 2003</a>, p.&#160;631.</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-58"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-58">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFSweat2015" class="citation book cs1">Sweat, Anthony (2015). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://rsc.byu.edu/coming-forth-book-mormon/hefted-handled-tangible-interactions-book-mormon-objects">"Hefted and Handled: Tangible Interactions with Book of Mormon Objects"</a>. In Largey, Dennis L.; Hedges, Andrew H.; Hilton, John III; Hull, Kerry (eds.). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://rsc.byu.edu/book/coming-forth-book-mormon"><i>The Coming Forth of the Book of Mormon: A Marvelous Work and a Wonder</i></a>. <a href="/wiki/Religious_Studies_Center" title="Religious Studies Center">Religious Studies Center</a>, <a href="/wiki/Deseret_Book" class="mw-redirect" title="Deseret Book">Deseret Book</a>. pp.&#160;43–59. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9781629721149" title="Special:BookSources/9781629721149"><bdi>9781629721149</bdi></a>. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20211205034935/https://rsc.byu.edu/coming-forth-book-mormon/hefted-handled-tangible-interactions-book-mormon-objects">Archived</a> from the original on December 5, 2021.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.atitle=Hefted+and+Handled%3A+Tangible+Interactions+with+Book+of+Mormon+Objects&amp;rft.btitle=The+Coming+Forth+of+the+Book+of+Mormon%3A+A+Marvelous+Work+and+a+Wonder&amp;rft.pages=43-59&amp;rft.pub=Religious+Studies+Center%2C+Deseret+Book&amp;rft.date=2015&amp;rft.isbn=9781629721149&amp;rft.aulast=Sweat&amp;rft.aufirst=Anthony&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Frsc.byu.edu%2Fcoming-forth-book-mormon%2Fhefted-handled-tangible-interactions-book-morm