<li id="cite_note-60"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-60">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFBushman2020" class="citation interview cs1"><a href="/wiki/Richard_Bushman" title="Richard Bushman">Bushman, Richard</a> (August 22, 2020). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.fromthedesk.org/richard-bushman-gold-plates/">"Richard Bushman on the Gold Plates"</a>. <i>From the Desk</i> (Interview). Interviewed by Kurt Manwaring. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20211102121352/https://www.fromthedesk.org/richard-bushman-gold-plates/">Archived</a> from the original on November 2, 2021.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=From+the+Desk&amp;rft.atitle=Richard+Bushman+on+the+Gold+Plates&amp;rft.date=2020-08-22&amp;rft.aulast=Bushman&amp;rft.aufirst=Richard&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fromthedesk.org%2Frichard-bushman-gold-plates%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABook+of+Mormon" class="Z3988"></span></span>
