<li id="cite_note-:32-184"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-:32_184-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFMurphy1999" class="citation journal cs1"><a href="/wiki/Thomas_W._Murphy_(anthropologist)" title="Thomas W. Murphy (anthropologist)">Murphy, Thomas W.</a> (Summer 1999). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/483199">"From Racist Stereotype to Ethnic Identity: Instrumental Uses of Mormon Racial Doctrine"</a>. <i>Ethnohistory</i>. <b>46</b> (3): 451–480. <a href="/wiki/ISSN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISSN (identifier)">ISSN</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.worldcat.org/issn/0014-1801">0014-1801</a>. <a href="/wiki/JSTOR_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="JSTOR (identifier)">JSTOR</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/483199">483199</a>. <a href="/wiki/PMID_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="PMID (identifier)">PMID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/20499476">20499476</a> &#8211; via JSTOR.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Ethnohistory&amp;rft.atitle=From+Racist+Stereotype+to+Ethnic+Identity%3A+Instrumental+Uses+of+Mormon+Racial+Doctrine&amp;rft.ssn=summer&amp;rft.volume=46&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.pages=451-480&amp;rft.date=1999&amp;rft.issn=0014-1801&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F483199%23id-name%3DJSTOR&amp;rft_id=info%3Apmid%2F20499476&amp;rft.aulast=Murphy&amp;rft.aufirst=Thomas+W.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F483199&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABook+of+Mormon" class="Z3988"></span></span>
